name: MysticWho
description: I'm running a node for Chainbase, the world's largest omnichain data network, integrating all blockchain data into a unified ecosystem. Chainbase provides transparent data interoperability for the AI era and aims to create a decentralized data economy with advanced AI capabilities. Join me in contributing to this network, which supports over 15,000 developers and 8,000 project partners, managing over 500 billion data calls
